Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比火龙快多…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成长为人真是个可悲的故事啊
